reviewText:
Unfortunately, I have to say that I'm dissatisfied with the Muhammad Ali DVD set in that the first DVD (his early years) did not work at all and that was the one I was most looking forward to watching. The others in the set are fine but the first one just did not play at all . This is very unusual . I've always been satisfied with products.
  Stephen Rapp

It's the whole thing. Quality is 6 to 9 out of ten but the fights are all there.

No regrets
roger
